OL,6,FA mum and dad have been found guilty
OL,7,Fof causing or allowing serious
OL,8,Fphysical harm to their baby son after
OL,9,Fhe suffered a bleed on the brain.
OL,11,FJordan Carrie was accused of shaking
OL,12,Fthe boy at his girlfriend Keeleigh
OL,13,FWatts' home in Rednal, Birmingham, in
OL,14,FJune 2020.
OL,16,FA trial at Birmingham Crown Court
OL,17,Fheard how people were concerned over
OL,18,FCarrie's handling of the baby and that
OL,19,Fhe had referred to him as a 'sp**,
OL,20,Fr****d and t***' on one occasion.
