OL,6,FThe pair had been in a relationship
OL,7,Ffor a couple of months before Watts
OL,8,Ffell pregnant. Watts lived at her
OL,9,Fmother's home at Roseleigh Road,
OL,10,FRednal, where Carrie stayed two nights
OL,11,Fa week and slept in a bunk bed with
OL,12,Fher.
