OL,6,FTheir baby suffered serious injuries
OL,7,Fon the morning of 13 June 2020, up
OL,8,Funtil which he had been 'healthy' and
OL,9,F'developing normally'.JProsecutor
OL,10,FJennifer Knight KC said: "Sometime
OL,11,Fbefore 9:50am, he became seriously
OL,12,Fill. He was having difficulty
OL,13,Fbreathing, appeared very pale and very
OL,14,Ffloppy. An ambulance was called.
