OL,6,F"He was taken to Birmingham Children's
OL,7,FHospital where he had an MRI scan. It
OL,8,Frevealed there was bleeding across the
OL,9,Fsurface of his brain and within the
OL,10,Fspaces of his brain."JThe infant also
OL,11,Fhad a lot of blood around his spinal
OL,12,Fcolumn and in his eyes, the court
OL,13,Fheard. Experts concluded he had
OL,14,Fsuffered a deliberate injury to his
OL,15,Fhead which in their view had been
OL,16,Fcaused by him being shaken.
