OL,6,FAt one stage Watts' mother, who 'gave
OL,7,Fher daughter a lot of support', warned
OL,8,Fher not to leave the child alone with
OL,9,FCarrie, the court had heard. A
OL,10,Fneighbour also claimed to have seen
OL,11,Fhim throwing the baby up into the air
OL,12,Fand catching him in the garden
OL,13,Fmultiple times.JMs Knight said: "What
OL,14,Fpeople noticed was that Jordan Carrie
OL,15,Fhad a heavy-handed approach."
