OL,6,FOn the morning in question, the
OL,7,Fdefendants alerted Watts' grandfather,
OL,8,Fwho also lived at the home, that their
OL,9,Fbaby was floppy. They asked their
OL,10,Fneighbour for help and an ambulance
OL,11,Fwas called.JThe couple were
OL,12,Fsubsequently arrested at the
OL,13,Fchildren's hospital later that day.
OL,14,FWatts initially told police that
OL,15,FCarrie was 'attentive' and their
OL,16,Frelationship was 'good'.
