OL,4,Callowing' baby son's brain injury
OL,6,FShe claimed her son fell ill while she
OL,7,Fwas in the kitchen washing bottles and
OL,8,Fshe heard him 'screaming' in the
OL,9,Fliving room.JBut Watts changed her
OL,10,Faccount to match Carrie, who claimed
OL,11,Fthey had been in the kitchen together.
OL,13,FIn a later police interview, she
OL,14,Fchanged her version of events claiming
OL,15,Fher partner was 'aggressive' and had
OL,16,Fpunched and kicked her as well as
OL,17,Fstruck her in the stomach with a bat
OL,18,Fwhile she was pregnant.
