OL,6,FWatts went on to say she was 'scared'
OL,7,Fof Carrie, who 'had outbursts every
OL,8,Ffew weeks and told her he would take
OL,9,Ftheir baby away if she did not stay
OL,10,Fwith him', the court heard.JShe told
OL,11,Fofficers on the morning of 13 June she
OL,12,Fhad actually been upstairs when Carrie
OL,13,Fcalled her on the phone to say
OL,14,F'something was wrong' with their baby.
